    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>eo</ex></expan> Merc<supplied reason="lost">urio</supplied> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iuval</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Atr</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">Ac</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>ceptus cives Tr<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ev</abbr><ex>eri</ex></expan> ne</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/><expan><abbr>gotiator</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> ex v<supplied reason="lost">oto</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="6"/>posue<supplied reason="lost">runt</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei nicht aneinanderpassende Fragmente mit dem linken Rand des Inschriftfeldes. Modern ergänzt. Z. 3: VA-, ET-Ligatur; Z. 6: VE-Ligatur. (B): Wagner: Z. 3/4: Zeilenfall nicht angegeben; Steinmetz: Z. 6: posue[runt]; Krier: Z. 1: In h(onorem); Z. 3: et C(aius); Z. 6: pos[uerunt ---].</p>
            </div>
